node.text:
I appreciate the pretty little cards that you took time to make for me, but know my little ones, you are my greatest gifts. I will always remember the first time I laid eyes on you and held you in my arms. That love and joy that swelled up in my heart, made me complete. Thank you for making me your mom and needing me always, through all those sleepless nights, tantrums and daily chaos. Thank you for showing me what it is to love selflessly and to give whole-heartedly. Thank you for constantly pushing my buttons and making me work on my patience.  Thank you for loving me despite my many shortcomings. In your eyes, I know I will always be perfect. Because of you, the simple moments in life are now more beautiful than before. 
Thank you for giving me a greater purpose in life. I’m blessed and forever grateful ❤️ #happymothersday

node.text:
2019, you have been nothing but awesome. Good and bad, we took things in stride because everything happens for a reason. Biggest milestone- having little Luke join our family! Thank you all for the love and positivity you gave here on this page.

Here’s wishing you and your loved ones a Happy New Year. To more adventures in 2020!

Love,
The Loks

node.text:
The alarm might not wake them up but the sound of Koko Krunch Cookie cereal certainly will!

Filled with mini-choco chips and made from wholegrain wheat, the Koko Krunch Cookie cereal contains dietary fibre and group B vitamin that get the kids ready for the day! Did I mention that it is also now koala bear-shaped 🐨 Even Luke loves to snack on it without milk!

Available at all leading supermarkets and selected online stores. #NestleKokoKrunchSG @nestlebreakfastcerealssg #sp

node.text:
Here with our favourite auntie and uncle who make the most delicious meepok (fishball noodles).

The lockdown and heightened alerts have been tough on our frontline community whom despite their fears, anxiety and at times unwarranted discrimination, have continued to persevere and carry on their work to bring normality to our daily lives.

Serving us with comfort food, they are a part of our essential workforce that brings hope and strength to all Singaporeans.

Support our frontliners by writing messages of encouragement and appreciation on the Digital Appreciation Board here - https://www.appreciate.gov.sg/

#SGunited #ForYourCourage #sp @wearemajulah

node.text:
About time Luke gets his little man cave! His loving sisters played a huge part in dressing up his room. We customized a classic striped wall paper (delicate stripes in grey blue) from @hello.circus Installation was a breeze and gave our blank walls a nice subtle touch!

#littlemancave #roommakeover
